headline: Jazz Icons Jools Holland OBE and Jamie Cullum Set Sail with Cunard in 2025
summary: Cunard is setting the tempo for music collaborations in 2025 with globally renowned jazz artists Jools Holland OBE and Jamie Cullum* headlining exclusive performances on board Queen Victoria next year.
